        "ggMnsicOai9_text": "<p>When archaeologists translated old Japanese medical texts, they found something unexpected: <strong>a natural oil used by samurai warriors to protect their scalp and beards from outbreaks under the sweaty armor.</strong><br>&nbsp;</p><p>This <strong>Samurai Oil</strong> kept their skin healthy for centuries… until it was forgotten by history.</p>",
