        "ggX3ivkvMH2_text": "<p>Unlike common beard oils (coconut, argan, jojoba) that actually provide food for fungus, Camellia oil’s unique fatty acid profile makes it fungus-resistant. Starving the fungus and stopping the production of dandruff.</p>",
